verbose_text: Plasma levels of oxidized DNA and RNA, quantified as plasma levels of multiple oxidative stress markers including 8-hydroxyguanosine from RNA, 8-OHdG from DNA, and 8-hydroxyguanine, were examined.
evidence: levels of multiple oxidative stress markers including 8-hydroxyguanosine from RNA, 8-OHdG from DNA, and 8-hydroxyguanine
